profile:
McLean's Construction is proud to specialize in the professional installation of ICF Foundations.  Our reputation is built on quality installations, integrity and customer satisfaction.  

Why choose ICF? The bottom line is ICF provides a higher quality structure and insulation for your home. Benefits include: 

◇ a higher insulation R value - great for Muskoka winters 

◇ reduced heating and cooling costs

◇ better sound barrier from outside noise

◇ reinforced structure

◇ more environmentally friendly

Let us build you a strong and insulated foundation for your home!  

Serving the Muskoka area.  Fully licensed and insured.  All work is guaranteed.

Call Colin at 705-783-3582 for your free quote
